					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204470" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;" >Decibelles</a></span> <span class="odate time_1432370466 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 May 2015 08:41</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2301576">
									

<p>Whether this happened or not, the way you tell this story is perfect and the flow and awkward pacing bring a sense of dread and validity it. Certainly, I had regretted reading this, but I did it more for the curiousity of the man in the blue suit. I was not disapponted.</p>

							</div>

								
					
