				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204470" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;" >DarkStuff</a></span> <span class="odate time_1494279446 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">08 May 2017 21:37</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2814829">
									

<p>Is it weird to say that this doesn't sound like a psychopath, and more like a really jaded dude really not wanting this guy to kill himself? I mean, after saying something like that to a guy, do you <em>really</em> expect him to still jump?</p>
<p>Seems like just an asshole giving someone some perspective on life in a weird, twisted way. Like all I can imagine if the guy did jump is this guy going &quot;Aw shit, really didn't expect that.&quot;</p>
<p>That really comes in the line &quot;Why would you care? You're dead.&quot;</p>

							</div>

								
					
