						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,4245606)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-4245606">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser deleted" data-id="3419959"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--images/avatars/default/a16.png" alt=""/>(account deleted)</span> <span class="odate time_1557591240 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">11 May 2019 16:14</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4245606">
									

<p>Yeah, thought the same. He improvised to scare the dude from jumping. But like&#8230;it was a wrong move. There's 50/50 chance when you say what this guy said. Like&#8230;do you really expect someone with severe depression to care about what will happen? Do you really expect someone you don't know cares? I'm saying this from my point of view, because if it were me on that roof, I'd jump just to do the opposite of what the stranger is trying to make me do. You know &quot;cut off the nose to spite your face.&quot; And I think there are other people like me, who are willing to hurt themselves in the long run just to prove somebody wrong.</p>

							</div>

										<div class="signature">
					<hr class="signature-separator"/>
					

<p><span style="color:violet"><tt>Ego sum mortuus</tt></span></p>

				</div>
					
					
